---
import GeneralHero from "../components/global/GeneralHero.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import {seo} from "../lib/config.json"
---

<Layout title={seo.privacy.title} description={seo.privacy.description}>
    <GeneralHero title="Privacy Policy" />

    <section class="terms-container m-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>At <strong>Crown Cars</strong>, we prioritize your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our services.</p>
            
            <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, contact details, payment information.</li>
                <li><strong>Vehicle Rental Data:</strong> Rental history, preferences, and feedback.</li>
                <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, and device information.</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>To process bookings and payments securely.</li>
                <li>To improve our customer service and rental experience.</li>
                <li>To comply with legal requirements and prevent fraud.</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>3. Data Protection & Security</h3>
            <p>We implement strict security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.</p>
            
            <h3>4. Sharing Your Information</h3>
            <p>We do not sell your data. However, we may share it with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Legal authorities if required.</li>
                <li>Payment processors for secure transactions.</li>
                <li>Partner service providers to enhance rental experiences.</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>5. Your Rights & Choices</h3>
            <p>You can access, update, or delete your personal data by contacting us. You may also opt out of marketing communications.</p>
            
            <h3>6. Changes to This Policy</h3>
            <p>We may update this policy periodically. Any changes will be posted on our website.</p>
            
            <h3>7. Contact Us</h3>
            <p>If you have any questions about this policy, please contact <strong>Crown Cars</strong> customer support.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
